FBIS4-14936 "drsov065_f_94021" FBIS-SOV-94-065 Daily Report 4 Apr 1994 National Affairs Crimean Broadcasting Staff Protests Decree Crimean Broadcasting Staff Protests Decree WS0404161194 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network in Ukrainian 1400 GMT 4 Apr 94 WS0404161194 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network Ukrainian BFN [Text] At a meeting today, representatives of Crimean radio and television protested against [Crimean President] Yuriy Meshkov's decree discharging Krym Broadcasting Company President Valeriy Astakhov from his duties. Participants in today's meeting emphasized that the decree was an insult to the company staff and ignored their opinions. There was a unanimous decision to lodge a protest against Yuriy Meshkov's decree. The protest has been sent to the Ukrainian president, the president of the Ukrainian Broadcasting Company, and the Ukrainian and Crimean Supreme Councils.
